import { Favorite, MoreVert, Share } from '@mui/icons-material'
import { Avatar, Box, Card, CardActions, CardContent, CardHeader, CardMedia, Collapse, IconButton, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const Feed = () => {
    return (
        <Box flex={4} p={2}>
            <Card >
                <CardHeader
                avatar={
                    <Avatar sx={{ bgcolor: "red"}} arial-label="recipe">

                    </Avatar>
                }
                action={
                    <IconButton arial-label="settings">
                        <MoreVert />
                    </IconButton>
                }
                title="Shrimp and Chorizo Paella"
                subheader="September 14, 2016"
                />
                <CardMedia 
                component="img"
                height="194"
                image="/static/images/cards/paella.jpg"
                alt="Paella dish"
                />
                <CardContent>
                    <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                        This impressive paella is a perfect party dish and a fun meal to cook togrther with your guests. Add 1 cup of frozen peas along with mussels, if you like.
                    </Typography>
                </CardContent>
                <CardActions disableSpacing>
                    <IconButton aria-label="add to favourites">
                        <Favorite/>
                        </IconButton>
                        <IconButton arai-label="share">
                            <Share />
                            </IconButton>
                </CardActions>
                <Collapse in={expended} timeout="auto" unmountOnExit>
                    <CardContent>
                        <Typography paragraph>Method:</Typography>
                        <Typography paragraph>
                        Heat 1/2 cup of the broth in a pot until simering , addn satfrom and set aside for 10 minutes.    
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography paragraph>
                        Heat 1/2 cup of the broth in a pot until simering , addn satfrom and set aside for 10 minutes.    
                        Heat 1/2 cup of the broth in a pot until simering , addn satfrom and set aside for 10 minutes.    
                        Heat 1/2 cup of the broth in a pot until simering , addn satfrom and set aside for 10 minutes.    
                        Heat 1/2 cup of the broth in a pot until simering , addn satfrom and set aside for 10 minutes.    
                        Heat 1/2 cup of the broth in a pot until simering , addn satfrom and set aside for 10 minutes.    
                        Heat 1/2 cup of the broth in a pot until simering , addn satfrom and set aside for 10 minutes.    
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography>
                            set aside off of the heat to let rest fro 10 minutes, and then serve.
                        </Typography>
                        </CardContent>
                    </Collapse>
            </Card>
            </Box>
    )
}

export default Feed
